'''2007年溫布頓網球錦標賽男子單打決賽'''是[[2007年溫布頓網球錦標賽|2007年溫布頓網球錦標賽]][[2008年溫布頓網球錦標賽男子單打比賽|男子單打比賽]]中的一場網球冠軍比賽。這場賽事是[[拿度與費達拿對戰史|拿度與費達拿對戰史]]中的一部分，世界排名第一的[[罗杰·费德勒|罗杰·费德勒]]對上世界排名第二的[[拉斐尔·纳达尔|拉斐尔·纳达尔]]。經過三小時又四十五分鐘後，罗杰·费德勒以 7–6<sup>(9–7)</sup>, 4–6, 7–6<sup>(7–3)</sup>, 2–6, 6–2獲得勝利。

這場比賽被認為是1980年溫布頓網球錦標賽男子單打決賽以來最經典的一場男子單打決賽<ref name="The New York Times">{{cite web|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2007/07/09/sports/tennis/09tennis.html?mabReward=csesort:w&contentCollection=Homepage&t=qry312#/federer+nadal+wimbledon/from20070701to20071201/&_r=0&action=click&region=Masthead&module=SearchSubmit&url=http://query.nytimes.com/search/sitesearch/?action=click&pgtype=Homepage&pagewanted=print|title=Federer Wins His Fifth Wimbledon Title in a Row|publisher=The New York Times|date=2007-07-09|accessdate=2014-04-16|archive-date=2020-11-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124063322/https://www.nytimes.com/2007/07/09/sports/tennis/09tennis.html?mabReward=csesort:w&contentCollection=Homepage&t=qry312#/federer+nadal+wimbledon/from20070701to20071201/&_r=0&action=click&region=Masthead&module=SearchSubmit&url=http://query.nytimes.com/search/sitesearch/?action=click&pgtype=Homepage&pagewanted=print|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/tennis/6280788.stm|title=Federer Wins Historic Fifth Title|publisher=The BBC|date=2007-07-09|accessdate=2014-04-16|archive-date=2019-05-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190524152017/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/tennis/6280788.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==背景==
[[罗杰·费德勒|罗杰·费德勒]]與[[拉斐尔·纳达尔|拉斐尔·纳达尔]]被認為是網球歷史中最佳的一組對戰組合<ref name="asgoodasitgets">{{cite news| publisher= ''International Herald Tribune'' ([[Associated_Press|Associated Press]])| title= Federer-Nadal rivalry as good as it gets| url= http://www.iht.com/articles/ap/2008/07/07/sports/TEN-On-Tennis-Rafa---Roger.php| date= 2008-07-07| accessdate= 2009-02-14| archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20090301014437/http://iht.com/articles/ap/2008/07/07/sports/TEN-On-Tennis-Rafa---Roger.php| archivedate= 2009-03-01| deadurl= no}}</ref><ref name="moveoverborgmac">{{cite news | first = Paul | last = Weaver | title = Move over McEnroe and Borg, this one will run and run in the memory | url = https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2008/jul/07/wimbledon.tennis4 | publisher = ''The Guardian'' | date = 2008-07-07 | accessdate = 2009-02-14 | location = London | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090123004930/http://www.guardian.co.uk/sport/2008/jul/07/wimbledon.tennis4 | archivedate = 2009-01-23 | deadurl = no }}</ref><ref name="asgoodassportgets">{{cite news | first = Martin | last = Flanagan | title = Federer v Nadal as good as sport gets | publisher = ''The Age'' | url = http://www.theage.com.au/news/tennis/federer-v-nadal-as-good-as-sport-gets/2008/07/11/1215658132528.html | date = 2008-07-12 | accessdate = 2009-02-14 | language =  | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090204175302/http://www.theage.com.au/news/tennis/federer-v-nadal-as-good-as-sport-gets/2008/07/11/1215658132528.html | archivedate = 2009-02-04 | deadurl = no }}</ref><ref name="bodo-rivalry!">{{cite web|url=http://tennisworld.typepad.com/tennisworld/2009/01/tj.html|title=Rivalry!|last=Bodo|first=Peter|date=2009-01-30|work=Peter Bodo's Tennisworld|publisher=Tennis.com|accessdate=2009-02-14|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090211061027/http://tennisworld.typepad.com/tennisworld/2009/01/tj.html|archivedate=2009-02-11|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref name="macgregor">{{cite web|url=http://sports.espn.go.com/espn/page2/story?page=macgregor/090203&sportCat=tennis|title=Greatest rivalry of the 21st century?|last=MacGregor|first=Jeff|date=2009-02-03|publisher=ESPN.com|accessdate=2009-02-14|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090212160857/http://sports.espn.go.com/espn/page2/story?page=macgregor%2F090203&sportCat=tennis|archivedate=2009-02-12|deadurl=no}}</ref>他們參加[[2007年溫布頓網球錦標賽|2007年溫布頓網球錦標賽]]時，這兩人取得過去9項[[網球大滿貫|大滿貫]]冠軍。

费德勒當時已連續獲得四次溫布頓網球錦標賽男子單打冠軍，企圖追平[[比約恩·博里|比約恩·博里]]連續獲得五次溫布頓網球錦標賽男子單打冠軍的歷史紀錄。

另一個方面來看，纳达爾已經連續奪得三屆[[法國網球公開賽|法國網球公開賽]]冠軍，試圖連續奪得法國網球公開賽與溫布頓網球錦標賽二項賽事冠軍。纳达爾當時對戰费德勒為8勝4負領先。

